OL,3,CSurprise fall in inflation eases
OL,4,Cpressure on the chancellor, for now
OL,6,FITV News Economics Editor Joel Hills
OL,7,Fdiscusses if the dip in inflation is a
OL,8,Ftemporary reprieve.
OL,10,FThe headline annual rate of inflation
OL,11,Fin the UK fell by more than expected
OL,12,Flast month, easing to 2.5% in December.
OL,14,FAt the very moment the markets have
OL,15,Fbegun to fret about the UK's economic
OL,16,Fprospects and the sustainability of
OL,17,Fthe government's finances, prices have
OL,18,Fstarted to behave in way the Bank of
OL,19,FEngland predicted once again.
