OL,3,CSurprise fall in inflation eases
OL,4,Cpressure on the chancellor, for now
OL,6,FA blizzard of recent bad news blew out
OL,7,Fthis morning when the Office for
OL,8,FNational Statistics published the
OL,9,FConsumer Prices Index. The chancellor
OL,10,Fand the Bank appear to be back in
OL,11,Fcontrol of the things that matter, for
OL,12,Fnow at least.
OL,14,FUK bond yields have fallen slightly
OL,15,Fthis morning as investors purchased
OL,16,Fgovernment debt again, the pound has
OL,17,Fstabilised.
OL,19,FA temporary reprieve? Almost certainly.
