OL,11,FThe drop in inflation last month was
OL,12,Fdriven by airfares as well as hotel,
OL,13,Frestaurant, alcohol and tobacco prices
OL,14,F- these things are volatile and are
OL,15,Flikely to rebound.
OL,17,FAnd there's still plenty of upward
OL,18,Fpressure on prices.
