OL,3,CSurprise fall in inflation eases
OL,4,Cpressure on the chancellor, for now
OL,6,F"Core" inflation, which strips out
OL,7,Ffood and energy prices, faded.
OL,9,FThe Bank has said for some time that
OL,10,Finflation in the services sector of
OL,11,Fthe UK economy - a good proxy for pay
OL,12,Fgrowth - has been far too high for
OL,13,Fcomfort.
OL,15,FLast month, Services inflation in the
OL,16,FUK fell by more than expected to 4.4%.
OL,17,FThat's still in uncomfortable
OL,18,Fterritory but is also the lowest level
OL,19,Ffor almost three years and undoubtedly
OL,20,Fencouraging.
