OL,6,FInvestors are betting on just two
OL,7,Finterest rate cuts in 2025. Next
OL,8,Fmonth, it's possible the Bank will
OL,9,Fsignal that markets are being over-
OL,10,Fanxious.
OL,12,FThe sharp rise in the government's
OL,13,Fborrowing costs, which began in
OL,14,FDecember but gathered pace in the last
OL,15,Fweek, has been alarming.
OL,17,FThe UK was not alone, the bond sell-
OL,18,Foff was global, but there's no
OL,19,Fquestion the UK government debt was
OL,20,Fperceived as a riskier bet than French
OL,21,For German.
