OL,6,FThe surprise fall in inflation will
OL,7,Fease pressure on the chancellor but if
OL,8,Fbond yields remain at these elevated
OL,9,Flevels the pressure will return in the
OL,10,Fweeks ahead, as households and
OL,11,Fbusinesses start to see their
OL,12,Fborrowing costs rise incrementally too.
OL,14,FIndeed, it may return tomorrow when we
OL,15,Ffind out how the economy performed in
OL,16,FNovember.
